01:01:12.410 --> 01:01:17.540
what you're doing and how you're thinking
about new things, new books to write, Frank,

01:01:17.540 --> 01:01:20.740
or work you're doing at Google, Chris.

01:01:20.740 --> 01:01:25.700
And I'd just love to--. Maybe I'll start with
Frank 'cause you've got a furtive mind and

01:01:25.700 --> 01:01:29.980
you're interviewing people. Is it who or is
it what?

01:01:29.980 --> 01:01:41.390
&gt;&gt;Frank Rose: Sure. I mean, this is sort of
