01:01:47.390 --> 01:01:55.550
naturally. And a few weeks ago, I had brunch
with this guy who was down from Boston who

01:01:55.550 --> 01:01:57.330
had just graduated from BU.

01:01:57.330 --> 01:02:07.770
His name is Nate Goldman. And he had done
a, he had spent two years as an undergrad,

01:02:07.770 --> 01:02:16.570
putting together for no credit or anything
this War of the Worlds type zombie experience

01:02:16.570 --> 01:02:20.970
[panel members chuckle]that took place over
a variety of different media. Primarily, his

01:02:20.970 --> 01:02:22.240
college radio station.

01:02:22.240 --> 01:02:29.180
Also he got people to dress up in the streets
