01:07:59.021 --> 01:08:03.910
there are microphones here, or we're a relatively
small audience, so just shout your question

01:08:03.910 --> 01:08:09.940
out if you've got any. Please.

01:08:09.940 --> 01:08:57.940
&gt;&gt;FEMALE AUDIENCE MEMBER #1: I was talking
that I work with Lance and I've worked with

01:08:57.940 --> 01:09:01.259
him on a couple of projects and he definitely
gives up authorship and he starts small, which

01:09:01.259 --> 01:09:02.259
is fantastic.

01:09:02.259 --> 01:09:03.259
So, he's always tweaking things as he's going
through a process. I work for OgilvyEntertainment

01:09:03.259 --> 01:09:04.259
on trying to harness social media and gaming
