01:12:10.777 --> 01:12:13.269
much smaller platforms and start building
an audience.

01:12:13.269 --> 01:12:20.079
And that is a huge way in for a lot of people
that didn't have a way in before. So, I think

01:12:20.079 --> 01:12:21.079
it's a big opportunity.

01:12:21.079 --> 01:12:28.070
&gt;&gt;Ted Hope: I mean, if you look at Marvel
